    <abstract>
      <t>The Local Mobility Anchor (LMA) and Mobile Access Gateway (MAG) are the key entities to realize system function of Proxy Mobile IPv6 (PMIPv6). It is critical to provide LMA/MAG reliability in the event of a LMA/MAG becoming failed or overloaded. This document provides a mechanism of LMA/MAG failure detection and service switching for failed or overloaded entities.</t>
